---
title: Lemon Ricotta Pancakes with Syrup & Crème plus a Kale-Orange Salad
description: Some special someone in your life got a sweet tooth? Try this delicious brunch-inspired meal on them. Start with decadent lemon ricotta pancakes and a dollop of zesty crème fraîche. Next, you’ll serve up a lovely kale salad with oranges and creamy feta on the side. Whether you break out the special plates or enjoy brunch in your PJs, we guarantee your boo or bae will be feeling the love.
